install git in the machine to clone the files from Github repository.
  yum install git

install python pip to run various dependencies such as boto3/flash
  yum install python3-pip

Configure AWS to associate with bedrock
  configure aws
  access key-id --
  access key --
  region "mention your default region"

Install various dependencies by using pip3 command
  pipv3 install boto3 "version name"
  pipv3 install Flash "version name"

pipv3 install -r requirements.txt --- this command install all softwares mentioned in the file - requirements
